<br>
First question depends on the DM. My DM just allows us to give us whatever stats we want, as long as he thinks they're fair and make sense.<br>
<br>
Question about death is: Usually, unless there's a damned good reason for it, and I use &quot;damned&quot; literally, if you die you are dead forever. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm25.showMessageRange?topicID=16.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm25.showMessageRange?topicID=16.topic&start=41&stop=60>3</a><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm25.showMessageRange?topicID=16.topic&start=61&stop=80>4</a><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm25.showMessageRange?topicID=16.topic&start=81&stop=97>5</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm25.showPrevMessage?topicID=16.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm25.showNextMessage?topicID=16.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm25.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=16.topic&index=40><img src=http://216.40.211.42/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm25.emailToFriend?topicID=16.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm25.threadControl?topicID=16.topic><img src=http://216.40.211.42/images/dagger.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm25.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=16.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ft